    "body": "There are also inconsistencies in groupby behaviour (0.19.1):\r\n\r\n```\r\n>>> df = pd.DataFrame({'a': np.zeros(0, dtype='int'), 'b': np.zeros(0, dtype='int')})\r\n\r\n>>> df\r\nEmpty DataFrame\r\nColumns: [a, b]\r\nIndex: []\r\n\r\n>>> df.dtypes\r\na    int64\r\nb    int64\r\ndtype: object\r\n\r\n>>> df.groupby(level=0).mean()\r\nEmpty DataFrame\r\nColumns: [a, b]\r\nIndex: []\r\n\r\n>>> df.groupby(level=0).quantile(0.5)\r\nEmpty DataFrame\r\nColumns: []\r\nIndex: []\r\n```"
